pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Just view and edit, without Delete and Add permissions

pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Custom permission level used to ensure that Corporate and ordinary News Owners / Editors can send out News Digests

pnp:RoleDefinition.Name: Add and Edit Items (custom)
pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Custom permission level used to ensure that Corporate and ordinary News Owners / Editors can send out News Digests

pnp:RoleDefinition.Name: Manage Hierarchy
pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Can create sites and edit pages, list items, and documents.

pnp:RoleDefinition.Name: Restricted Read
pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Can view pages and documents, but cannot view historical versions or user permissions.

pnp:RoleDefinition.Name: Approve
pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Can edit and approve pages, list items, and documents.

pnp:RoleDefinition.Name: Portal Site Owner Permissions
pnp:RoleDefinition.Description: Can view, add, update, delete, approve, and customize.
